{"id": 1350, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得“长大”这件事好在哪？", "description": "小时候有小时候的好，长大也有长大的快乐（题图来自：Anna Ryzhova）", "record_count": 4637, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161127225016s3faCb1V2YiMEpcB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-30T03:00:27Z", "options": [{"id": 137984, "content": "可以自己掌控自己的生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851271}, {"id": 138240, "content": "享受自己管理自己的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847285}, {"id": 137985, "content": "知道的更多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 845568}, {"id": 138241, "content": "爸妈离不离婚可以不用顾及我了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806539}, {"id": 137986, "content": "就算失去某人，也能好好活着", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772313}, {"id": 138242, "content": "好在可以帮父母承担压力，", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851886}, {"id": 137987, "content": "没人管着了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107551}, {"id": 137988, "content": "可以从家里搬出来住☺️", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112307}, {"id": 137989, "content": "有自己的选择与自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847293}, {"id": 138245, "content": "可以自己觉得去哪儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 822580}, {"id": 139269, "content": "可以自己养活自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853793}, {"id": 137990, "content": "目前来说是——经济独立", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819538}, {"id": 138246, "content": "找女朋友做自己爱做的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674726}, {"id": 151814, "content": "可以自己规划，出去旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896757}, {"id": 137991, "content": "花钱不用顾忌那么多", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851308}, {"id": 138247, "content": "想要一场说走就走的旅行！\n然而这并不现实\n????", "image": "img/option/option/20161201000900S8GKWNJ92MrQYAbT", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851394}, {"id": 147975, "content": "非常不想长大 不想懂事 不想知道这个社会的黑暗\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 881555}, {"id": 137992, "content": "发现绝大部分人的话你都不必听", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851304}, {"id": 151560, "content": "难道是可以啪啪啪？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895036}, {"id": 137993, "content": "可以当一个和我爸爸不一样的爸爸", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851297}, {"id": 137995, "content": "长大变孙子", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225838}, {"id": 139531, "content": "懂得童年有多美好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855075}, {"id": 137996, "content": "人格更独立更自由了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 743197}, {"id": 138252, "content": "能拥有感受更多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851904}, {"id": 139788, "content": "可以一个人…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655402}, {"id": 137997, "content": "让你明白小时候的自己有多天真。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 845000}, {"id": 138253, "content": "长大就可以过自己羡慕的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 502960}, {"id": 137998, "content": "生活如此多娇", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829644}, {"id": 138254, "content": "又开始怀念小时候了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851912}, {"id": 137999, "content": "自由做自己想做的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773694}, {"id": 138255, "content": "小时候玩泥巴的岁月", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851912}, {"id": 138000, "content": "花自己赚的钱 去更多的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833255}, {"id": 138256, "content": "自由和爱情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851915}, {"id": 138001, "content": "哈哈哈哈，长大会赚钱了～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851327}, {"id": 138257, "content": "知道了关你屁事 和 关我屁事", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832038}, {"id": 138002, "content": "自己的事情自己想，更有想法了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829785}, {"id": 138258, "content": "可以不听爸妈的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851924}, {"id": 138003, "content": "有些方面变得自由，而有些方面却又更不自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209905}, {"id": 138259, "content": "之前做儿子，现在做孙子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745079}, {"id": 138004, "content": "可选的赚钱的方式多了，搬砖都可以赚几百啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836749}, {"id": 138260, "content": "好在有自我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132367}, {"id": 142356, "content": "不用为了高考赶作业", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863210}, {"id": 138005, "content": "长大可以赚钱了，赚大钱!", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836749}, {"id": 138261, "content": "开始怀念小时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766293}, {"id": 138006, "content": "长大可以赚钱了，对，赚大钱!", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836749}, {"id": 138262, "content": "长大一点也不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849960}, {"id": 138007, "content": "好在终于没有时间去后悔了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712373}, {"id": 138263, "content": "可以有能力照顾家人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851932}, {"id": 138008, "content": "知道生活有多么不容易了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783313}, {"id": 138264, "content": "长大了可以谈恋爱了  可以自己赚钱买喜欢的物品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769171}]}